    {
      "id": "seq_403_minister_appears",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "左大臣",
      "text": "今宵は歌にて、若君の心を量る。雪の庭に、軽き言葉は落ちて消えようぞ。",
      "next": "seq_404_judge_intro"
    },
    {
      "id": "seq_404_judge_intro",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "判者",
      "text": "一番、題は『雪』。ただ白しと言うなかれ。白きものに、見えぬ心を映してこそ歌。",
      "next": "seq_405_topic_snow"
    },
    {
      "id": "seq_405_topic_snow",
      "type": "choice",
      "text": "一番『雪』。どの趣で詠む？",
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "雪の白さに、御簾の向こうの声を重ねる",
          "next": "seq_406_topic_wait_intro",
          "effects": { "fantasySynchro": 8, "utakaiPrepScore": 2 }
        },
        {
          "text": "庭が白くてきれいだと素直に詠む",
          "next": "seq_406_topic_wait_intro",
          "effects": { "fantasySynchro": 3, "utakaiPrepScore": 1 }
        },
        {
          "text": "寒いので早く帰りたいと詠む",
          "next": "seq_406_topic_wait_intro",
          "effects": { "realityEgo": 5, "brainErosion": 4, "utakaiPrepScore": 0 }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "seq_406_topic_wait_intro",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "判者",
      "text": "二番、題は『待つ』。急く心は真なれど、歌は心を投げつける器にあらず。",
      "next": "seq_407_topic_wait"
    },
    {
      "id": "seq_407_topic_wait",
      "type": "choice",
      "text": "二番『待つ』。返歌にふさわしい心は？",
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "待つ時間そのものを、月の移ろいとして詠む",
          "next": "seq_408_topic_return_intro",
          "effects": { "fantasySynchro": 7, "utakaiPrepScore2": 2 }
        },
        {
          "text": "なぜ遅いのかと相手を責める",
          "next": "seq_408_topic_return_intro",
          "effects": { "brainErosion": 10, "utakaiPrepScore2": 0 }
        },
        {
          "text": "会いたい気持ちは隠さず、季節の景に預ける",
          "next": "seq_408_topic_return_intro",
          "effects": { "realityEgo": 4, "fantasySynchro": 6, "utakaiPrepScore2": 2 }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "seq_408_topic_return_intro",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "判者",
      "text": "三番、題は『帰る』。この題に、今宵のすべてが潜む。",
      "next": "seq_409_topic_return"
    },
    {
      "id": "seq_409_topic_return",
      "type": "choice",
      "text": "三番『帰る』。あなたは何を詠む？",
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "帰る朝だけを願う歌",
          "next": "seq_410_trigger_utakai",
          "effects": { "realityEgo": 12, "utakaiReturnTone": 1 }
        },
        {
          "text": "帰らぬ夢だけを願う歌",
          "next": "seq_410_trigger_utakai",
          "effects": { "fantasySynchro": 14, "utakaiReturnTone": 2 }
        },
        {
          "text": "帰る袖にも、残る香があると詠む歌",
          "next": "seq_410_trigger_utakai",
          "effects": { "realityEgo": 8, "fantasySynchro": 8, "utakaiReturnTone": 3 },
